properties.name: Paolo Nutini's Hometown
properties.description: Posted by NutiniPaisley, Scotland20-year-old singer/ songwriter blessed with a soulful, passionate voice and the natural gift of being able to tell a story in a song. Like many of the truly inspired singer/songwriters before him, Nutini has absorbed the soul of classic artist from both sides of the Atlantic and channeled it into something original, captivating, and dynamic. Despite their Italian name, the Nutini family has lived in Paisley, Scotland for at least four generations. Paolo\'s great-grandfather opened the fish and chip shop in Paisley which his parents now run. Paolo\'s musical education began with his late grandfather, who introduced him to Scottish folk songs as well as a wide range of other styles.
